metadata.name: Oh, bunny!
metadata.description:
1/1 hand-drawn artwork "Oh, bunny!" is the first part of the whole collection "Wild souls" with wild animals.

Our souls are wild as animals. We all always personalize ourselves with some animal. And I want to suggest you to collect one of your favorite totem!

Here is a bunny. Sweet and fun white wild rabbit. It's cute but don't forget still wild:))
